Our coalition keeps growing - 2 amazing non-profits endorsed the Principles this week: @ChoiceinAging, which provides services to seniors & people with disabilities in Contra Costa, Solano, Napa, & Sac counties, & @SVatHome which advocates for affordable housing in Silicon Valley
We've made it even easier to endorse the Seamless Transit Principles as an organization or company.  Just fill out this online form:  https://t.co/edaFWBAOZz

Fossil Free Mid-Peninsula and @350sv are the latest groups to endorse the Seamless Transit Principles! We're now up to *55*!
